Title: Life
All Day Event: 'What makes a good leader?  What makes a person willingly work or follow another person- and what are the qualities that make us successful as leaders and managers?  If you've ever wanted to know how to be a more effective manager- how you can attract people who want to work for you- or just how to be more effective at managing your group- this is an introduction to what makes those people special- and rise above the rest.'
